if GS_Type70 = 0 \ | GS_Type70 = MARKER_ONELINE\ | GS_Type70 = MARKER_TRIANGLE1\ | GS_Type70 = MARKER_TRIANGLE2\ | GS_Type70 = MARKER_TWOLINES1\ | GS_type70 = MARKER_TWOLINES2\ | GS_type70 = MARKER_ARROW\ | GS_Type70 = MARKER_LIMA_STYLE \ then ! epsilon = - EPS if SYMB_MIRRORED then epsilon = + EPS endif _1stQuarter = totalRotate < (45 + epsilon) | totalRotate > (315 + epsilon) _2ndQuarter = totalRotate > (45 + epsilon) & totalRotate < (135 + epsilon) _3rdQuarter = totalRotate > (135 + epsilon) & totalRotate < (225 + epsilon) _4thQuarter = totalRotate > (225 + epsilon) & totalRotate < (315 + epsilon)

textblock "Textblock1" 0, _text_anchor, 0, AC_TextCharWidthFactor_1, AC_TextCharSpaceFactor_1, 1, "Paragraph1"
if (iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 135 and totalRotate < 270) and not(SYMB_MIRRORED)) |\ (iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and abs(totalRotate - 270) < EPS) then add2 0, -hos endif

if (iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 135 and totalRotate < 270) and not(SYMB_MIRRORED)) |\ (iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and abs(totalRotate - 270) < EPS) then del 1 endif
else if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL then if t1 <> "" & t2 <> "" and (text_anchor = 9 or text_anchor = 7) then add2 0, _markerSize endif endif

gosub 2000
if text_readable & text_rotangle > 90 + EPS & text_rotangle < 270 + EPS then del 5 else del 3 endif

gosub 2000

if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_ALIGNED and (totalRotate > 90 and totalRotate <= 270) and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") then add2 0, -hos-dsc endif

if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and (((totalRotate - EPS) <= 45) or (totalRotate-EPS) >= 315) and SYMB_MIRRORED and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") then add2 0, hos+dsc endif
if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL then if ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 135 and totalRotate < 270) and not(SYMB_MIRRORED) |\ ((totalRotate-EPS) > 225 and (totalRotate+EPS) < 315) and (t1 = "" or t2 = "") |\ (abs(totalRotate-315) < EPS) and SYMB_MIRRORED then add2 0, -hos endif endif

if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_ALIGNED and (totalRotate > 90 and totalRotate <= 270) and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") then del 1 endif
if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_HORIZONTAL and ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 45 and totalRotate < 270) and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") and not(SYMB_MIRRORED) |\ iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_HORIZONTAL and ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 135 and totalRotate + EPS < 315) and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") and SYMB_MIRRORED then del 1 endif
if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL and (((totalRotate - EPS) <= 45) or (totalRotate-EPS) >= 315) and SYMB_MIRRORED and (t1 <> "" & t2 <> "") then del 1 endif if iTextRotation = MARKER_TEXTROTATION_VERTICAL then if ((totalRotate + EPS) >= 135 and totalRotate < 270) and not(SYMB_MIRRORED) |\ ((totalRotate-EPS) > 225 and (totalRotate+EPS) < 315) and (t1 = "" or t2 = "") |\ (abs(totalRotate-315) < EPS) and SYMB_MIRRORED then del 1 endif endif endif endif

poly2_ 5, 3, mcr*sin(-45), mcr*cos(45), 1, 0, 0, 901, mcr*sin(45), mcr*cos(45), 3001, 0, _markerSize / 2, 1, mcr*sin(-45), mcr*cos(45), 1 endif circle2 0,0, mcr
